IB/core: Convert core to use bitfield for caps

Remove query_protocol callback

Use the new Core Capability bits for:

rdma_protocol_*
rdma_cap_ib_mad
rdma_cap_ib_smi
rdma_cap_ib_cm
rdma_cap_iw_cm
rdma_cap_ib_sa
rdma_cap_ib_mcast
rdma_cap_af_ib
rdma_cap_eth_ah

